description: Kidville Inc. operates various facilities for newborns and children up to six years old in the United States. It offers gym, music, art, dance, enrichment, and pre-school alternative classes and programs; and day camp for toddlers, pre-schoolers, and big kids, as well as seasonal and holiday camps. The company also hosts birthday parties; and operates an indoor playspace, a boutique, salon, and a cafe. In addition, it conducts events for Kidville members. The company was formerly known as Longfoot Communications Corp. and changed its name to Kidville Inc. in August 2008. Kidville Inc. is based in New York, New York.
